   Dilectus Lusitanus de venae sectione. c. xi. Artic. 1. p. 145. in his Treatise of Venae-sectione: and Epiphanius Ferdinandus, and Aemilius Campolongus. Neither is it to be questioned, but that this is the common practise of all Italy;
   Epiphanius Ferdinandus cas. Medic. 78. Aemil. Campol. de variolis, c 413. so that I shall cite no more of that Nation.
